Array methods

// Arrays.toString(array)                   get String print of array in one line (otherwise you can not get print of all
                                            elements in one print command)
// Arrays.sort(array);                      to sort array in natural order
// Arrays.sort(arrayName, fromIdx, toIdx);
// Arrays.equals(array1, array2)            check if both of arrays have same order of values
// Arrays.fill(array, value );              fill the array with provided value
// Arrays.binarysearch(array, value);       return index of given value in array, otherwise returns -1

